# Firefox OS page : http://www.allizom.org/b/firefoxos
;Bringing the Open Web to mobile devices
Ukuzisa izixhobo zeemfonomfono eziphathwayo zeWebhu Evulekileyo


;Welcome to a new, open and powerful mobile world!
Wamkelekile kwihlabathi elitsha, elivulekileyo nelinamandla leemfonomfono eziphathwayo!


;Firefox OS enables the Open Web as a platform for mobile devices. We’re making innovation possible by driving the development of new Web standards.
IFirefox OS ikuvulela iWebhu Evulekileyo njengeqonga lezixhobo zeemfonomfono eziphathwayo. Senza ukuqulunqa ubugcisa obutsha kwenzeke ngokukhuthaza uphuhliso lwemigaqo emitsha yeWebhu.


;New Web standards
Imigaqo Emitsha YeWebhu


;Firefox OS will produce an implementation of these new Web standards to free mobile platforms from the encumbrances of the rules and restrictions of existing proprietary platforms.
IFirefox iza kubangela ukusetyenziswa kwale migaqo mitsha yeWebhu kumaqonga asimahla eemfonomfono eziphathwayo kwimiqobo nemida yemithetho yamaqonga obunini akhoyo.


;Freedom from proprietary mobile platforms
Ukukhululeka kumaqonga obunini eemfonomfono eziphathwayo


;We’re collaborating with <abbr title="Original Equipment Manufacturer">OEM</abbr>s and carriers directly, giving them more influence to meet the specific needs of their users and market. Users and developers aren’t locked in to one platform, so they can access their info and use apps across multiple devices.
Sisebenzisana kunye <abbr title="Nomvelisi Wokuqala Wesixhobo">OEM</abbr> nabathuthi bempahla ngokuthe ngqo, nto leyo ebanika impembelelo engakumbi ukuze bahlangabezane neemfuno zabasebenzi neemarike zabo. Abasebenzisi nabaphuhlisi abavalelekanga kwiqonga elinye, banokukwazi ke ukuhlola inkcazelo yabo baze basebenzise ii-apps kwizixhobo ezininzi.


;Customization for <abbr>OEM</abbr>s and operators
Ukulungiselela <abbr>OEM</abbr> nabalawuli


;<abbr>OEM</abbr>s and operators will be able to provide content and services across their entire device portfolio, regardless of OS. And they will be able to customize user experiences, manage app distribution and retain customer attention, loyalty and billing relationships.
<abbr>OEM</abbr> nabalawuli baza kunikezela umbandela neenkonzo kudidi lwesixhobo sabo, nokuba yeyiphi na i-OS. Yaye baza kukwazi ke ngoku ukulungiselela amava abasebenzisi, balawule ukuhanjiswa kwee-app zabo baze bathimbe ingqalelo yabathengi, ukunyaniseka neentlawulo zabo.


;Opportunities for developers
Amathuba abaphuhlisi


;Using HTML5 and the new Mozilla-proposed standard APIs, developers everywhere will be able to create amazing experiences and apps. Developers will no longer need to learn and develop against platform-specific native APIs.
Ngokusebenzisa i-HTML5 nomgaqo omtsha ondululwayo weMozilla i-APIs, abaphuhlisi kwiindawo zonke baza kukwazi ukudala amava nee-apps ezingayiwayo. Abaphuhlisi abasayi kufuneka bafunde baze baphuhlise ii-APIs ezenzelwe amaqonga athile.


;Consumer freedom
Inkululeko yabathengi


;Consumers who use devices powered by Firefox OS won’t be locked into one specific platform giving them more choice, flexibility and freedom. With Firefox OS, the Web is the platform.
Abathengi abasebenzisa izixhobo ezigunyaziswe yiFirefox OS abayi kubopheleleka kwiqonga elinye kunoko baya kufumana ukhetho olungakumbi, bakwazi ukutshintshatshintsha yaye bakhululeke. NgeFirefox OS, iWebhu iba liqonga.
